
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhang-trill-p2mp-bfd-02.txt'>
    <title>"TRILL Support of Point to Multipoint BFD", Mingui Zhang, Juniper Networks, Vengada Govindan</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhang-trill-p2mp-bfd-02.txt</link>
    <description>Point to multipoint (P2MP) BFD is designed to verify multipoint connectivity.  This document specifies the support of P2MP BFD in TRILL.  Similar to TRILL point-to-point BFD, BFD Control packets in TRILL P2MP BFD are transmitted using an RBridge Channel.</description>
    <dc:date>2015-05-12T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
